            Daily reading combines stable sign pattern with date and weekday modulation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="astral-mini-card">
          <p class="astral-mini-label">Method transparency</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-200">
